https://unity3d.com/legal/privacy-policy
4. We use AppLovin ads, the related privacy policy is described by AppLovin, see more details in
https://www.applovin.com/privacy/
5. We use Mopub ads, the related privacy policy is described by Mopub, see more details in
https://www.mopub.com/en/legal/privacy
6. We use ADColony ads, the related privacy policy is described by ADColony, see more details in
https://www.adcolony.com/privacy-policy/
7. We use Pangle ads, the related privacy policy is described by Pangle, see more details in
https://www.pangleglobal.com/privacy
8. We use Tapjoy ads, the related privacy policy is described by Tapjoy, see more details in
