D. Our Policies About Children
We never knowingly or willingly collect any personal data concerning children under 16 years of age.
E. Your Rights and How to Access, Update, and Manage Your Personal Information
European Countries Users Rights
If you are located in the European Countries, you have the following data protection rights by sending us mail to "myfuncookie@gmail.com" with the subject line "European Rights Request", we will process your request ASAP in 1 day to 2 week:
1. You can access or request deletion of your personal information.
2. You can correct or update your personal information.
3. If we have collected and processed your personal information with your consent, then you can withdraw your consent at any time.
4. You can ask us to restrict processing of your personal information.
California Users Rights
If you are a California resident, you may be able to exercise additional rights granted by California law in relation to the Personal Information that we have collected from you. When you want to exercise your right, please email to "myfuncookie@gmail.com" with the subject line "California Rights Request", we will process your request ASAP in 1 day to 2 week.
Brazilian Users Rights
If you are a Brazilian resident, you may be able to exercise additional rights granted by Lei Geral de Proteção de Dados (LGPD) in relation to the personal information. When you want to exercise your right, please email to "myfuncookie@gmail.com" with the subject line "Brazilian Rights Request", we will process your request ASAP in 1 day to 2 week.
F. Data Security and Retention
We implement reasonable measures to help secure the information we collect. We retain the data we collect for up to 24 months.
G. CHANGES TO THIS PRIVACY POLICY
We reserve the right, at our sole discretion, to change, modify or otherwise alter this Policy at any time. You can always check the latest version of our Privacy Policy on the games. You must review this Policy on a regular basis to keep
            yourself apprised of any changes. If you do not agree to any modifications to this Policy, your sole recourse is to immediately stop all use of the games. Your continued use of any games following the posting of any modifications
            to this Policy will constitute your acceptance of the revised Policy. Please note that none of our employees or agents has the authority to vary any of our Policies.
G. CONTACT US
If you have any questions or comments about this policy or our privacy practices, or to report any violations of the Policy or abuse of our games, services or site, please contact us at
myfuncookie@gmail.com
.